{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketProtocol\/conditionCheck(condition:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketProtocol"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checks on the readiness of "},{"code":"socket","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to perform operations."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The operations specified in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"condition"},{"type":"text","text":" are checked for and masked"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"against the currently-satisfied conditions on "},{"code":"socket","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is returned."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"conditionCheck"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"condition"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"IOCondition","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"IOCondition","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that on Windows, it is possible for an operation to return","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"wouldBlock","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" even immediately after"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_condition_check()"},{"type":"text","text":" has claimed that the socket is ready for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"writing. Rather than calling "},{"code":"g_socket_condition_check()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and then","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"writing to the socket if it succeeds, it is generally better to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"simply try writing to the socket right away, and try again later if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the initial attempt returns "},{"code":"wouldBlock","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is meaningless to specify [err](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/err or [hup](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/hup in condition;","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these conditions will always be set in the output if they are true."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This call never blocks."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socketprotocol\/conditioncheck(condition:)"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO14SocketProtocolPAAE14conditionCheck0D04GLib11IOConditionVAH_tF","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"conditionCheck","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"condition","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"IOCondition","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV","text":"IOCondition"}],"title":"conditionCheck(condition:)"},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SocketProtocol/conditionCheck(condition:)":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Checks on the readiness of ","type":"text"},{"code":"socket","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to perform operations."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The operations specified in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"condition"},{"type":"text","text":" are checked for and masked"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"against the currently-satisfied conditions on "},{"code":"socket","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". The result","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is returned."}],"title":"conditionCheck(condition:)","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socketprotocol\/conditioncheck(condition:)","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketProtocol\/conditionCheck(condition:)","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"conditionCheck"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"condition","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"IOCondition","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"IOCondition","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SocketProtocol":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketProtocol","title":"SocketProtocol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socketprotocol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"code":"GSocket","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a low-level networking primitive. It is a more or less"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct mapping of the BSD socket API in a portable GObject based API.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It supports both the UNIX socket implementations and winsock2 on Windows.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SocketProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SocketProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/